      "methodology": "Composite average pass@1 across DeepSWE, Terminal-Bench v2, and SWE-Atlas-QnA",
      "score_range": "Expressed as percentage (0-100%); top agent (Codex GPT-5.6 Sol xhigh) = 78.7%",
      "note": "This is an AGENT-level score (model + harness + config), NOT a standalone model score. Different harnesses/configs produce different scores for the same model.",
