    },
    "important_caveats": [
      "Intelligence Index and Coding Agent Index are COMPLETELY DIFFERENT metric systems with DIFFERENT scales.",
      "Intelligence Index: 0-65 range (model-level composite benchmark score).",
      "Coding Agent Index: 0-100% range (agent-level pass@1 on coding tasks).",
      "They CANNOT be directly compared on a single dual-axis bar chart.",
      "Coding Agent Index scores depend on the agent harness (Codex, Claude Code, Cursor CLI, etc.) and effort level (none/low/medium/high/max/xhigh).",
      "Some models in the Intelligence Index may NOT appear in the Coding Agent Index because they haven't been tested with any agent harness."
    ],
